{"tid":656032,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"張敬軒有無資格喺eason之後再上神台？","createTime":"2018-05-07T01:33:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-15T14:05:54.000Z","uid":60793,"like":232,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":68,"replies":[{"pid":"e7aae41eb1904a5f3fb64ced6d07e79396a4e557","tid":656032,"uid":60793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T01:33:38.000Z","msg":"張敬軒大家應該都好熟悉 作品質素同數量都無需多講 <br />\n對歌唱事業都好認真 比eason好 <br />\n演出發揮穩定 穩定地好<br />\n上神台應該都無乜異議？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n題外話<br />\n除左張敬軒 有無人可以擔到香港/廣東歌大旗？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac2ce1c7c566581ae01eaec39a67bc28f2219201","tid":656032,"uid":156511,"like":18,"dislike":181,"score":-163,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T01:37:51.000Z","msg":"佢憑乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7888413ecf7b2ae5807db94e26ddf46868e8e8a","tid":656032,"uid":555,"like":5,"dislike":62,"score":-57,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T01:39:03.000Z","msg":"gem"},{"pid":"47257676da1ebff74f18c4adc8de3d791622eea9","tid":656032,"uid":22694,"like":72,"dislike":4,"score":68,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T01:41:45.000Z","msg":"太認真上唔到神枱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要似eason鳩下鳩下先得"},{"pid":"e5aadeb45f10eeab3ef59ffecc23335bb8e2ab7b","tid":656032,"uid":69013,"like":84,"dislike":79,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T01:45:29.000Z","msg":"唔知點解，Eason 唱既歌有一種入心入肺既力量，可以剖析自我，或使自我釋懷。<br />\n但張敬軒既歌最多都係「好聽」，但仲係少左果種感覺。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e04f893f8a74a41c98e35108c2f14db5709e8e5","tid":656032,"uid":80719,"like":9,"dislike":61,"score":-52,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T01:47:15.000Z","msg":"冇，最多係特色歌手，唔係一線歌手個隻感覺"},{"pid":"ab2025698bd9346d481b9435aca8499f1d85db27","tid":656032,"uid":181318,"like":96,"dislike":2,"score":94,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T02:10:31.000Z","msg":"如果佢唔係一線 唔通坤哥係咩"},{"pid":"121200c35406c70e73c95f33db4cd37d27330758","tid":656032,"uid":60793,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"ab2025698bd9346d481b9435aca8499f1d85db27","tid":656032,"uid":181318,"like":96,"dislike":2,"score":94,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T02:10:31.000Z","msg":"如果佢唔係一線 唔通坤哥係咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T02:14:39.000Z","msg":"一線就係一線嫁喇 不過唔知幾時有資格或者有潛力上神台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2887ae77d181d3c7e16a1bcbea02979263b8ba56","tid":656032,"uid":3333,"like":68,"dislike":2,"score":66,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T02:37:21.000Z","msg":"Eason似係天才型，又食煙唔保養把聲，但唱歌又好鬼好聽（但狀態近年唔太穩定）<br />\n張敬軒就係努力專注文藝，音樂，感覺上有心機好多，但經典歌冇Eason多，你睇兩位係香港開演唱會既場數都差一節。<br />\n<br />\n利申（張敬軒Fans)"},{"pid":"985b3521515e32aee35232a4f423bd47f14bdb98","tid":656032,"uid":129221,"like":4,"dislike":22,"score":-18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T02:38:44.000Z","msg":"奶共 垃圾"},{"pid":"3a2eb8f38ec1af68b3b9a79d396ab427594e3472","tid":656032,"uid":162920,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T02:44:43.000Z","msg":"廣東歌 冇人聽啦 再神級都係早幾年既事"},{"pid":"5b3a577cc7099a443eddd33bb648bea2b67ca222","tid":656032,"uid":97523,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T02:52:15.000Z","msg":"冇後浪就自動上神台架啦<br />\n<br />\n你唔服佢但又搬唔到第個出黎<br />\n<br />\n香港依家有邊個夠軒仔鬥？"},{"pid":"b147ec73e52d6e6448aa4060c35e8cae141150b4","tid":656032,"uid":39215,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T02:52:53.000Z","msg":"蜀中無大將"},{"pid":"95196abb537a9dcfcab2a2e0aba10736c5381025","tid":656032,"uid":60793,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"5b3a577cc7099a443eddd33bb648bea2b67ca222","tid":656032,"uid":97523,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T02:52:15.000Z","msg":"冇後浪就自動上神台架啦<br />\n<br />\n你唔服佢但又搬唔到第個出黎<br />\n<br />\n香港依家有邊個夠軒仔鬥？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T02:55:50.000Z",